DESCRIPTION:This peer group will meet Tuesdays at 12 PM EST for the live as
 pect of your Advanced Figma course.\n\nThere are 1 total units in this cour
 se and each week we’ll be covering a new unit. In addition to lessons and p
 roject work for each unit\, you’ll also meet with your mentor and peer grou
 p weekly.\n\nBefore this session\, you should:\n\n1. Complete the exercises
  for that week’s unit\n2. Note down any questions and topics of discussion 
 you have based on the week’s course materials\n\nIf you are unable to join 
 this week:\nPlease let your mentor know if you are unable to join the sessi
 on – we strongly encourage you to attend each week\, as they are one of the
  most valuable parts of the course.
